{"tid":2083281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！ 國師陳雲宣布退出香港社運 ！","createTime":"2020-06-28T15:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T01:39:41.000Z","uid":118346,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"65b48e2bfa5cac6a05b4d9b2991a57e3f3a20655","tid":2083281,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:38:32.000Z","msg":"陳雲：我宣布退出香港社運。香港大部分人不需要我的社運理論指導，他們將香港的命運、也是他們自己的命運交了給泛民港獨，將香港推入國際政治鬥爭的黑洞。香港是一艘馬力巨大的超級大船，進入漩渦是沒問題的，進入黑洞是吉凶難料。<br />\n過去十年來，我做的善意的、也是有利維護中港關係、祖國與香港共榮的1234步驟的工作，總是被泛民港獨騎劫，做了惡意的、破壞中港關係的5678步驟的工作。本來主張維護中港共榮關係的本土派，也被泛民媒體騎劫和刻意宣傳，變成港獨派錯誤代表了本土派。泛民港獨得到大部分香港人的投票支持，他們贏了議席，輸掉香港。在現代社會，人民為大，我尊重大部分香港人要輸掉香港的決定。<br />\n我在2016年立法會選舉、主張「永續基本法」的議程失敗之後已經宣布退場，那是我在香港最後一次的政治行動，只是很多泛民港獨還以為我在場。<br />\n今後繼續我以往的學術研究、民間教育、時事評論、國學發揚和香港文化外傳工作，偶然做一些散文和小說創作。"},{"pid":"77bc8cfacdebb90956e0ce5ae5b39afb00c52a6b","tid":2083281,"uid":307619,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:39:45.000Z","msg":"瞓咗成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"75cae0e6c32a243fc440f2d7958df900ca21b698","tid":2083281,"uid":58209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:39:56.000Z","msg":"聽日又復出救港嫁啦 講黎把撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c90fa0479c43b7bb864bfd8d3ce6e3542c3efa98","tid":2083281,"uid":4780,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:40:05.000Z","msg":"好行唔送<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ddf9f2d1cf1ea58e7b63ac93c4b237b10140c6","tid":2083281,"uid":4387,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:41:41.000Z","msg":"驚撚左蟈安法？"},{"pid":"ec0a4c292b439adec5e59fba421d6bd0a0906f5a","tid":2083281,"uid":246878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"你估國安法會放過你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236938da1a00998603c0999934d365c2dae459dd","tid":2083281,"uid":172349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"時窮節乃見"},{"pid":"b208738bf300853f4d8daef094160733efdf785e","tid":2083281,"uid":20640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:42:11.000Z","msg":"一推國安法就縮返去老母塊閪度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n皇天擊殺喎"},{"pid":"15ce88d0b6d20ed8ec5a0e13ea4b243426b04e02","tid":2083281,"uid":276293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:42:36.000Z","msg":"拗底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee2b815341872a47c670638ea085cc7fc9f056b","tid":2083281,"uid":172349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"236938da1a00998603c0999934d365c2dae459dd","tid":2083281,"uid":172349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:42:10.000Z","msg":"時窮節乃見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:43:41.000Z","msg":"老燒移民 陳雲龜縮 黃洋達堅決反對港獨"},{"pid":"c12c2f79af83c0945b99b2c826cfa821b7808ab2","tid":2083281,"uid":137704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"又話自己係中共座上客"},{"pid":"0ef91ffe2d81bacac4193cb204da5c7f5b43df1f","tid":2083281,"uid":103156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:44:26.000Z","msg":"央視：退出政壇，難逃國安法懲罰。"},{"pid":"01778c858d83ec745af4c3aa44b0fb735cd4fab1","tid":2083281,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:45:43.000Z","msg":"佢有加入過咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6811b0e61eb8eed8fdb64b22ee7bfeee64cb82e3","tid":2083281,"uid":282445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T15:48:22.000Z","msg":"溫故知新：人地國師4年前已經退出過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D0QLcRV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD0QLcRV.p